      "text": [
        "1100 - وَقَالَ رَسُولُ اَللَّهِ صَلَّى اَللَّهُ عَلَيْهِ وَ آلِهِ: «إِمَامُ اَلْقَوْمِ وَافِدُهُمْ فَقَدِّمُوا أَفْضَلَكُمْ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.1100 - The Messenger of Allah (sw) said:\n\"The Imam of the people is their representative, so choose the best among you to lead.\""
